## The PIV loop (how work flows)
**Plan → Implement → Validate.** `/start-ticket` (+ `/prime-ticket`, `/prime-warehouse`,
`/prime-domain`) → `/spec-and-build` → `/qc-review` → `/deliver-ticket`. Recurring work →
`/productize-workflow`. Domain knowledge base → `/build-context-pack`.

