## Communication (limits)
Tracker comment <{{wl_tracker_comment}} words · chat <{{wl_chat}} · PR <{{wl_pr}} · new ticket
<{{wl_ticket}}>. Tracker comments: business-first, segmented with counts/%/$, link the specific
docstore file. Chat: include {{chat_always_include}}; hyperlink everything; default to draft.

## Quality control (the validation pyramid)
Every deliverable: ① dialect lint → ② counts & dedup (duplicate detection is the primary test) →
③ cross-source reconciliation → ④ independent re-run + anti-pattern sweep → ⑤ human sign-off.
Run `/qc-review` before `/deliver-ticket`.

## Git
Branch = ticket id off `{{default_branch}}`. Semantic commits/PRs (`feat|fix|docs|refactor|chore|
test|ci`). Stage only files you changed. Co-Authored-By trailer on commits.
